to this of our poor host!
There you are mistaken, Oakes; you took more in
mine;
for, when I made a will in your own favour, and
gave it to you to read, you tore it in two, and threw it
over-board
,
with your own hand.
Ay, that was an act of lawful authority. As your
superior
,
